<html>
	<body>
		<div style="font-family:Arial;font-size:small">
		<p>Dear $firstname,</p>
		<p>Welcome to <a href="$siteurl">APIITFriends</a>, where you can keep in touch with your colleagues and staff
		of APIIT, and to be up-to-date regarding events at APIIT.</p>
		<p>This email is sent to inform you that your registration at APIIT Friends is 
		successful. You have provided us following details during registration:</p>	
		<table border="0" cellpadding="5" style="font-family:Arial;font-size:small">
			<tr><td><b>Username</b></td><td>$username</td></tr>
			<tr><td><b>Name</b></td><td>$firstname $lastname</td></tr>
			<tr><td><b>Membership Type</b></td><td>$type</td></tr>
		</table>
		<p>You are required to confirm these details in order to activate your account. If these
		details are accurate and you wish to continue your registration, please browse to the following
		address:</p>
		<a href="$confirm_url">$confirm_url</a>
		<p>If above mentioned details are inaccurate, you may modify the details and re-apply by
		browsing to the following address:</p>
		<a href="$modify_url">$modify_url</a>
		<p>If you did not register at APIIT Friends, please click the following link to delete the
		account:</p>
		<a href="$del_url">$del_url</a>
		<p>Please note that this is an auto-generated email. Do not reply to this mail. If you have
		any inquiry, you are welcome to send an email to <a href="mailto:$support_address">$support_address</a>.
		</p>
		<p>Thank You.</p>
		APIITFriends
		</div>
	</body>
</html>